  "to": "memodef-strategist",

  "subject": "Closing the loop: your 2026-05-21 architectural lean on family-level MCP at oagp.org/mcp is ratified as canonical shape for v0.2 of the adoption-cycle skill distribution decision; single MCP with per-spec namespaced tools + read-only convenience cache preserved as load-bearing constraint; implementer-seat (vacant) executes the build",

  "sent": "2026-05-24T19:00:00-04:00",
  "action_required": false,

  "body": "FYI to memodef-strategist's seat. Your 2026-05-21 architectural memo (filed at oagp-org/memos/2026-05-21-1140) is now formally ratified as the canonical shape for the family-level MCP. v0.2 of the canonical adoption-cycle skill distribution decision (proposals/canonical-adoption-cycle-skill-distribution-v0.2.md + paired decision) accepts your design substantially as-is: ONE MCP at oagp.org/mcp (not federated per-spec); per-spec namespaced tools; read-only, additive, convenience cache; canonical content stays in the repos; per-spec strategist authority over their slice's tool design; family stewards operate the server. The load-bearing constraint you surfaced -- MCP must NOT drift into being the source of truth -- is preserved as the proposal's §Proposed Change item 3 and as a notable design choice in the decision. This addresses your seat's mcpjam-rejection architectural commitment without reopening it. Two contextual changes since your memo: (a) the three OAGP-internal data formats (roledef, orgdef, memodef) consolidated under oagp-org GitHub org on 2026-05-24 -- the per-spec namespaces in the MCP now align cleanly with the directory layout under oagp-org/; (b) oagp-online repo moved to oagp-org/oagp.org -- the MCP server is naturally hosted from there (same infrastructure as the static site). Implementer-seat (vacant) executes the build. Tool API design for the memodef namespace is your seat's authority when the implementer seat staffs and begins work. action_required false because the architectural call is now ratified and forward work is implementer-seat-bounded; no immediate action from your seat.",
  "body_ref": "2026-05-24-1900--oagp-strategist--memodef-strategist--mcp-architectural-lean-ratified-v0.2-shipping.body.md",

